block menu/about
	p You can create custom navigational menus for your website in #[+mark( 'nav', 'Appearance', 'Menus' )]. They may contain links to pages, categories, custom links or other content types. You can specify a custom menu item label, as well as other attributes.

	p Display menus on your website by assigning them to a predefined theme menu location, or you can also display them using "Navigation Menu" widget in your sidebars. The theme defines these menu locations for you:

	dl.list-default.has-quoted-terms
